T1  - The true meaning of David Ricardo’s four magic numbers
AU  - Maneschi, Andrea
JO  - Journal of International Economics
VL  - 62
IS  - 2
SP  - 433
EP  - 443
PY  - 2004
DA  - 2004/03/01/
SN  - 0022-1996
